Package TuitionManager

Class International

java.lang.Object
TuitionManager.Student
TuitionManager.International
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Comparable
public class International
extends Student
Class for International students, extends the Student class and inherits the properties. International students are students who are not from the country where the school exists.
